lenders.name: Jaspen
lenders.loan_because:
At Jaspen Papers, we love to support entrepreneurs who operate ethically, support their local communities, and believe in basic environmental stewardship. KIva Zip now allows us to contribute more to the U.S. small business community and support like-minded entrepreneurs who often struggle to obtain working capital from traditional means.

On Kiva.org, Jaspen Papers focuses on individual female entrepreneurs in the food industry or who own a viable small business. Often, they are denied financial capital because of their religion, ethnicity, gender, or geographical location.
